  "title": "Inside Sales Representative  #JK",
  "description": "<h3>⭐ <strong>Attractive Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Up to $800 monthly performance incentive</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Additional half-yearly performance bonus</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Basic salary up to $3,000</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5-day work week (location in Kallang)</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>AWS included</strong></p></li><li><p>Entitled to <strong>transport, medical, and dental allowances</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Long-term renewable contract</strong> with yearly increment</p></li><li><p><strong>Training provided – no experience required</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Opportunity to convert to permanent role</strong> based on performance</p></li><li><p>Exposure to <strong>Marketing & Sales teams</strong> to build strong communication and business skills</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Scope</strong></h3><p>The Inside Sales Representative will support the sales team by generating new leads through outbound calls to manufacturing contacts, introducing KEYENCE’s products and services.<br />👉 <strong>No product selling or deal closing is required.</strong></p><h3><strong>Ideal Profile</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Comfortable and confident making outbound phone calls</p></li><li><p>Fluent in spoken languages with good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Positive, motivated, and resilient attitude</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>GCE “O” Level</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Candidates with no experience are welcome</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Multiple positions available</strong><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, please send your latest resume to <strong>jinkai@talentsatwork.sg </strong>or WhatsApp me at <strong>98811690</strong>.</p><p></p><p>Talents@Work Pte Ltd (21C0501)</p><p>Tan Jin Kai (R23115830)</p><p></p></li></ul>",
